No photograph annexed.

No photograph annexed.

5) 'Photograph [of] 'Reminiscence of the Vyrnwy Valley', No 4. 'The Vyrnwy Valley' by Peter Ghent. View of valley with river covered by water lilies and rushes in foreground'.

No photograph annexed.

No photograph annexed.

No photograph annexed.
